{"id":294,"text":"Tesla电动车的电池采用了松下提供的NCA系列（镍钴铝体系）18650钴酸锂电池，整车的电池包分为60kW·h或者85kW·h两类（早期产品），","entities":[{"id":124,"label":"PAR","start_offset":31,"end_offset":41},{"id":125,"label":"MAT","start_offset":25,"end_offset":28},{"id":126,"label":"PAR","start_offset":45,"end_offset":48}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":296,"text":"85kW·h的Model S的电池单元一共运用了8142个18650锂电池，组装时首先将这些电池以单元、模组逐一平均分配，","entities":[{"id":147,"label":"PAR","start_offset":29,"end_offset":37}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":298,"text":"电池包内每一节18650钴酸锂电池两端均设有保险装置，每个电池片和电池砖都有保险装置，一旦发现某一单元内部出现问题，","entities":[{"id":157,"label":"PAR","start_offset":7,"end_offset":17},{"id":158,"label":"PAR","start_offset":22,"end_offset":26},{"id":159,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":3}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":299,"text":"保险装置就会将其切断与其他电池单元的联系，从而避免影响整体电池性能的情况出现。","entities":[{"id":167,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":4},{"id":168,"label":"PAR","start_offset":13,"end_offset":17}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":302,"text":"当然，保险装置是最后的一道屏障，当它切断的时候也就意味着某个电池单元出现了问题，如果涉及更换，整个电池包就可以以“模组”为单位进行更换。","entities":[{"id":148,"label":"PAR","start_offset":3,"end_offset":7}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":305,"text":"1、电池单体：在60kW·h的版本中，分真电池和电池填充两种。","entities":[{"id":169,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":6}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":306,"text":"2、母线牌：起到了连接电池的作用，将每组电池的正极和负极连接在一起，共有7种不同的规格。","entities":[{"id":129,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":5},{"id":133,"label":"PAR","start_offset":23,"end_offset":25},{"id":134,"label":"PAR","start_offset":26,"end_offset":28}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":307,"text":"3、隔层：隔层将电池与冷却管隔离并有绝缘的作用。","entities":[{"id":142,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":4},{"id":143,"label":"PAR","start_offset":5,"end_offset":7},{"id":144,"label":"PAR","start_offset":11,"end_offset":14}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":308,"text":"4、散热铜管：通过每一面与单体连接，将热量带出整个电池模组。","entities":[{"id":149,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":6}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":309,"text":"5、隔离板：在电池的顶盖上方，起到绝缘的作用。","entities":[{"id":155,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":5}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":310,"text":"6、BMU采集板：测量电压和温度。","entities":[{"id":160,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":8}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":311,"text":"7、熔丝：连接电池单体与母线牌，采用半导体中的黏结工艺，对于电池组装而言，这是非常难的工艺。","entities":[{"id":170,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":4}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":312,"text":"8、温度传感器：采集温度，其位置在冷却管的输入端和输出端。","entities":[{"id":130,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":7},{"id":131,"label":"PAR","start_offset":17,"end_offset":20}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":313,"text":"9、采样电压采集线束：采集电池电压，并有专门的固定的导线索引结构进行固定。","entities":[{"id":145,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":10}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":314,"text":"如下图所示，高压电池位于车辆下方，并通过34个螺栓将其固定在适当的位置，该螺栓将电池固定至车身和副车架。电池是底盘的受力部件，","entities":[{"id":150,"label":"PAR","start_offset":6,"end_offset":10}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":315,"text":"为汽车提供平坦的底面和很低的重心。高压电池提供了结构、空气动力学和操纵方面的优势。","entities":[{"id":156,"label":"PAR","start_offset":17,"end_offset":21}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":317,"text":"所有配置均使用锂离子18650电池。85kW·h电池包含16个模块，每个模块包含6个单元，每个单元包含74个单独的电池。","entities":[{"id":171,"label":"PAR","start_offset":7,"end_offset":17}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":319,"text":"每个模块都有自己的电池监视板（BMB），可监视每个电池单元的电压并从模块内的四个点对温度进行采样。","entities":[{"id":146,"label":"PAR","start_offset":9,"end_offset":14}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":320,"text":"BMB通过内部通信总线将此信息报告给电池管理系统（BMS）。然后，BMS使用此信息来管理高压电池温度和SOC。BMS通过动力总成（PT）CAN总线进行通信。","entities":[{"id":151,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":3},{"id":152,"label":"PAR","start_offset":18,"end_offset":24},{"id":153,"label":"PAR","start_offset":33,"end_offset":36}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":322,"text":"电池还包含B+和B-接触器、电流测量分流器和630A的保险丝。","entities":[{"id":161,"label":"PAR","start_offset":5,"end_offset":7},{"id":163,"label":"PAR","start_offset":8,"end_offset":13},{"id":164,"label":"PAR","start_offset":8,"end_offset":10},{"id":165,"label":"PAR","start_offset":14,"end_offset":21},{"id":166,"label":"PAR","start_offset":27,"end_offset":30}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":323,"text":"高压电池的作用是提供动力来驱动汽车并运行所有附件系统。它是车辆的主要能源。它向驱动逆变器提供直流电以驱动车辆，","entities":[{"id":172,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":4},{"id":173,"label":"PAR","start_offset":39,"end_offset":44}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":324,"text":"并向DC-DC转换器提供直流电以支持12V电气系统。DC-DC转换器还用作高压接线盒，将电流从高压电池分配到A\/C压缩机、冷却液加热器和机舱加热器。","entities":[{"id":135,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":10},{"id":136,"label":"PAR","start_offset":18,"end_offset":25},{"id":137,"label":"PAR","start_offset":37,"end_offset":42},{"id":138,"label":"PAR","start_offset":61,"end_offset":67},{"id":139,"label":"PAR","start_offset":68,"end_offset":73},{"id":140,"label":"PAR","start_offset":26,"end_offset":34},{"id":141,"label":"PAR","start_offset":54,"end_offset":60}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":443,"text":"一、电池的分类按照不同的能量来源方式，电池可以分为化学电池、物理电池及生物电池三大类。目前汽车行业运用的电池","entities":[{"id":414,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":25,"end_offset":29},{"id":415,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":30,"end_offset":34},{"id":416,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":35,"end_offset":39}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":444,"text":"基本都是化学电池，因此本文不对物理电池及生物电池做过多阐述。化学电池根据特性的不同，又可以分为一次电池、二次电池及燃料电池。","entities":[{"id":323,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":47,"end_offset":51},{"id":324,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":52,"end_offset":56},{"id":325,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":57,"end_offset":61}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":445,"text":"其中，一次电池也称为原电池，即使用后不能再行充电的电池（例如生活中使用的锌锰干电池）；","entities":[{"id":332,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":3,"end_offset":7},{"id":333,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":36,"end_offset":41}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":446,"text":"二次电池也被称作为蓄电池，即一次放电后可以再行充电使用的电池，我们生活中的充电宝\/手机以及汽车用电池都是属于这种类型；","entities":[{"id":336,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":0,"end_offset":4}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":447,"text":"燃料电池指正负极本身不含活性物质，活性材料为外部不断补充的电池，目前的氢燃料电池就是属于这一种。","entities":[{"id":306,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":0,"end_offset":4},{"id":307,"label":"PAR","start_offset":5,"end_offset":8},{"id":308,"label":"MAT","start_offset":12,"end_offset":16},{"id":309,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":35,"end_offset":40}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":448,"text":"抛开尚未成气候的燃料电池，目前的汽车动力电池基本都是二次电池，根据介质的不同，二次电池主要包含铅酸电池、镍镉电池、镍氢电池、锂离子电池、锂金属电池等。","entities":[{"id":372,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":8,"end_offset":12},{"id":373,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":18,"end_offset":22},{"id":374,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":26,"end_offset":30},{"id":375,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":39,"end_offset":43},{"id":376,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":47,"end_offset":51},{"id":377,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":52,"end_offset":56},{"id":378,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":57,"end_offset":61},{"id":379,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":62,"end_offset":67},{"id":380,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":68,"end_offset":73}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":450,"text":"作为汽车的启动电源，绝大部分汽车蓄电池都是铅酸电池，其正极为二氧化铅（PbO2），负极为纯铅，电解质为硫酸水溶液。","entities":[{"id":177,"label":"MAT","start_offset":30,"end_offset":34},{"id":178,"label":"PAR","start_offset":41,"end_offset":43},{"id":179,"label":"MAT","start_offset":44,"end_offset":46},{"id":181,"label":"PAR","start_offset":47,"end_offset":50},{"id":182,"label":"MAT","start_offset":51,"end_offset":56},{"id":183,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":21,"end_offset":25},{"id":245,"label":"PAR","start_offset":27,"end_offset":29}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":451,"text":"对于蓄电池为什么会选择铅酸，而不是用逐渐成主流的锂电池替代？原因有很多，包括技术成本、安全程度及电池寿命，但最主要的还是铅酸电池的低温性能，","entities":[{"id":219,"label":"MAT","start_offset":11,"end_offset":13},{"id":220,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":24,"end_offset":27},{"id":221,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":60,"end_offset":64}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":452,"text":"相比于锂电池，铅酸电池的低温性能更佳，在低温下锂离子电池的放电性能是处于衰减性递减的，零下10度就会迅速没电，","entities":[{"id":257,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":3,"end_offset":6},{"id":258,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":7,"end_offset":11},{"id":259,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":23,"end_offset":28}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":453,"text":"对应的是铅酸电池零下50度都能正常发动汽车。说完蓄电池，就不得不拉回正题，谈谈动力电池，目前市面上电动汽车基本上都采用的是锂离子电池（以下简称锂电池），","entities":[{"id":310,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":4,"end_offset":8},{"id":311,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":39,"end_offset":43},{"id":312,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":24,"end_offset":27},{"id":313,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":61,"end_offset":66},{"id":342,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":71,"end_offset":74}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":456,"text":"从上图我们可以看出，锂离子电池无论在体积能量密度还是质量能量密度上都具有很大的优势，且相对于锂金属电池更加安全。","entities":[{"id":184,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":10,"end_offset":15},{"id":185,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":46,"end_offset":51}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":457,"text":"这也是锂电池得以脱颖而出的一个重要原因。此外，相对于其他二次电池，锂电池还具有更优的寿命及环保表现。","entities":[{"id":222,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":3,"end_offset":6},{"id":223,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":33,"end_offset":36},{"id":334,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":28,"end_offset":32}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":458,"text":"三、锂电池的简介3.1锂电池工作原理锂离子电池一般是使用锂合金金属氧化物为正极材料、石墨为负极材料、使用非水电解质的一种二次电池。","entities":[{"id":260,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":2,"end_offset":5},{"id":261,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":18,"end_offset":23},{"id":262,"label":"MAT","start_offset":28,"end_offset":36},{"id":263,"label":"PAR","start_offset":37,"end_offset":39},{"id":264,"label":"MAT","start_offset":42,"end_offset":44},{"id":265,"label":"PAR","start_offset":45,"end_offset":47},{"id":266,"label":"MAT","start_offset":52,"end_offset":57},{"id":337,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":60,"end_offset":64}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":459,"text":"锂电池充电时，锂离子从正极脱嵌，向负极移动，嵌入负极；锂离子放电时，锂离子从负极脱嵌，向正极移动，嵌入正极。","entities":[{"id":314,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":0,"end_offset":3},{"id":315,"label":"PAR","start_offset":11,"end_offset":13},{"id":316,"label":"PAR","start_offset":17,"end_offset":19},{"id":317,"label":"PAR","start_offset":24,"end_offset":26},{"id":318,"label":"PAR","start_offset":38,"end_offset":40},{"id":319,"label":"PAR","start_offset":44,"end_offset":46},{"id":320,"label":"PAR","start_offset":51,"end_offset":53}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":460,"text":"3.2锂电池的分类锂电池按正极材料的不同，可以分为磷酸铁锂、锰酸锂、钴酸锂及三元材料。","entities":[{"id":381,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":3,"end_offset":6},{"id":382,"label":"MAT","start_offset":25,"end_offset":29},{"id":383,"label":"MAT","start_offset":30,"end_offset":33},{"id":384,"label":"MAT","start_offset":34,"end_offset":37},{"id":385,"label":"MAT","start_offset":38,"end_offset":42}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":463,"text":"钴酸锂，是最早实现商业化的锂电池正极材料，但其缺点是比容量太低、安全性差，成本也较高。","entities":[{"id":224,"label":"MAT","start_offset":0,"end_offset":3},{"id":225,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":13,"end_offset":16},{"id":226,"label":"PAR","start_offset":16,"end_offset":18}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":464,"text":"三元材料，分为镍钴锰（NCM，以蔚来为代表）和镍钴铝（NCA，以特斯拉为代表）两种，其中钴是三元锂必不可少的材料，","entities":[{"id":267,"label":"MAT","start_offset":7,"end_offset":10},{"id":268,"label":"MAT","start_offset":23,"end_offset":26},{"id":269,"label":"MAT","start_offset":44,"end_offset":45},{"id":270,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":46,"end_offset":49}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":465,"text":"因为钴本身是有毒性的，因此“少钴化”也是目前三元电池领域研究的一个课题。","entities":[{"id":343,"label":"MAT","start_offset":2,"end_offset":3},{"id":344,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":22,"end_offset":26}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":466,"text":"从成本、安全、性能等综合因素考量，目前市面上的动力电池主要以磷酸铁锂及三元锂电池为主。","entities":[{"id":386,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":23,"end_offset":27},{"id":387,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":30,"end_offset":34},{"id":388,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":35,"end_offset":40}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":467,"text":"四、动力电池的构造电动汽车的动力电池实际上是一个统称，包含电芯、模组以及电池包三个层级。","entities":[{"id":418,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":2,"end_offset":6},{"id":419,"label":"PAR","start_offset":29,"end_offset":31},{"id":420,"label":"PAR","start_offset":32,"end_offset":34},{"id":421,"label":"PAR","start_offset":36,"end_offset":39},{"id":422,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":14,"end_offset":18}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":468,"text":"电芯（Cell），可以充放电的锂离子电池基本单位，包含了正负极、隔膜及电解液，是电池氧化还原反应的进行空间。","entities":[{"id":186,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":2},{"id":187,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":15,"end_offset":20},{"id":188,"label":"PAR","start_offset":28,"end_offset":31},{"id":243,"label":"MAT","start_offset":32,"end_offset":34},{"id":244,"label":"MAT","start_offset":35,"end_offset":38}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":469,"text":"根据电芯封装形式不同，可以分为圆柱电芯、方形电芯及软包电芯。","entities":[{"id":227,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":4},{"id":228,"label":"PAR","start_offset":15,"end_offset":19},{"id":229,"label":"PAR","start_offset":20,"end_offset":24},{"id":230,"label":"PAR","start_offset":25,"end_offset":29}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":470,"text":"模组（Module），为了保护电芯免于受到外部热、振动等冲击，将一定数量的电芯连接在一起，放在一个框架中组成电池的组件。","entities":[{"id":271,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":2},{"id":272,"label":"PAR","start_offset":15,"end_offset":17},{"id":273,"label":"PAR","start_offset":37,"end_offset":39}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":471,"text":"电池包（Pack），是装入电动汽车中电池的最终形态，在模组的基础上装配电池管理系统（BMS）、电池冷却系统、线束、支架等零部件。","entities":[{"id":345,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":3},{"id":346,"label":"PAR","start_offset":35,"end_offset":41},{"id":347,"label":"PAR","start_offset":47,"end_offset":53},{"id":348,"label":"PAR","start_offset":54,"end_offset":56},{"id":349,"label":"PAR","start_offset":57,"end_offset":59}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":472,"text":"简而言之，三者的关系为，多个电芯组成模组，多个模组组成电池包，然后再总成装配至电动汽车上。","entities":[{"id":389,"label":"PAR","start_offset":14,"end_offset":16},{"id":390,"label":"PAR","start_offset":18,"end_offset":20},{"id":391,"label":"PAR","start_offset":23,"end_offset":25},{"id":392,"label":"PAR","start_offset":27,"end_offset":30}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":473,"text":"4.1什么是18650电芯？18650是锂电池（电芯）的一种型号，是由日本SONY公司当年定下的一种标准性的锂离子电池型号，","entities":[{"id":423,"label":"PAR","start_offset":6,"end_offset":13},{"id":424,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":20,"end_offset":23},{"id":425,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":54,"end_offset":59}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":475,"text":"18650电池具有成熟的配套产业链，成本低廉，是一种理想的锂离子电池，在消费电子领域得到了广泛的应用。","entities":[{"id":231,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":0,"end_offset":7},{"id":232,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":29,"end_offset":34}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":476,"text":"但18650电池容量较小，在动力电池领域应用时，往往需要上万只单体电池组合成为电池组，导致电池组的管理难度大幅上升。","entities":[{"id":276,"label":"PAR","start_offset":31,"end_offset":35},{"id":277,"label":"PAR","start_offset":39,"end_offset":42},{"id":278,"label":"PAR","start_offset":45,"end_offset":48},{"id":280,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":1,"end_offset":8},{"id":338,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":14,"end_offset":18}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":478,"text":"掀起了一场21700替换18650电池的风暴。相对于18650电池，21700电池的电量密度是目前世界上能量密度最高且成本最低的电池，","entities":[{"id":393,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":5,"end_offset":10},{"id":394,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":12,"end_offset":19},{"id":395,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":26,"end_offset":33},{"id":396,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":34,"end_offset":41}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":480,"text":"4.2什么是刀片电池？刀片电池是比亚迪于2020年3月29日发布的电池产品，可以称为超级磷酸铁锂电池。","entities":[{"id":191,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":6,"end_offset":10},{"id":192,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":11,"end_offset":15},{"id":193,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":42,"end_offset":50}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":481,"text":"之所以称为刀片电池，是因为它的排布方式像是刀片一样插入电池包内。","entities":[{"id":233,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":5,"end_offset":9},{"id":235,"label":"PAR","start_offset":27,"end_offset":30}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":482,"text":"这款刀片电池相比较三元锂电池来说，更加耐低温，并且它的电芯具有更大的散热面积，同时它能够匹配到较高的能量密度。","entities":[{"id":279,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":2,"end_offset":6},{"id":281,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":9,"end_offset":14},{"id":282,"label":"PAR","start_offset":27,"end_offset":29}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":484,"text":"相较传统电池包，“刀片电池”的体积利用率提升了50%以上，也就是说续航里程可提升50%以上，","entities":[{"id":397,"label":"PAR","start_offset":4,"end_offset":7},{"id":398,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":9,"end_offset":13}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":485,"text":"达到了高能量密度三元锂电池的同等水平，并且比三元锂有了更优的安全及寿命表现。","entities":[{"id":426,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":8,"end_offset":13},{"id":427,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":22,"end_offset":25}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":486,"text":"五、动力电池的主要参数5.1电池能量电池能量即电池储存的能量，能量（W·h，瓦时）=电压（V）*电池容量（A·h，安时），","entities":[{"id":327,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":2,"end_offset":6}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":497,"text":"5.4电池的一致性一致性是动力电池中的表现形式之一，同一规格型号的单体电池组成电池组后，","entities":[{"id":428,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":13,"end_offset":17},{"id":429,"label":"PAR","start_offset":33,"end_offset":37},{"id":430,"label":"PAR","start_offset":39,"end_offset":42}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":499,"text":"锂电池的一致性是指这些参数的趋同性，是一个相对概念。同一个电池包内的多串电芯，","entities":[{"id":236,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":0,"end_offset":3},{"id":237,"label":"PAR","start_offset":29,"end_offset":32},{"id":238,"label":"PAR","start_offset":36,"end_offset":38}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":504,"text":"包含了正极所用到的镍、钴、锰、锂等矿产，也包含了石墨、电解液、隔膜等材料。我国的锂资源比较丰富，但钴资源却很匮乏，","entities":[{"id":194,"label":"PAR","start_offset":3,"end_offset":5},{"id":195,"label":"MAT","start_offset":9,"end_offset":10},{"id":196,"label":"MAT","start_offset":11,"end_offset":12},{"id":197,"label":"MAT","start_offset":13,"end_offset":14},{"id":198,"label":"MAT","start_offset":15,"end_offset":16},{"id":199,"label":"MAT","start_offset":24,"end_offset":26},{"id":204,"label":"MAT","start_offset":40,"end_offset":41},{"id":205,"label":"MAT","start_offset":49,"end_offset":50},{"id":241,"label":"MAT","start_offset":31,"end_offset":33},{"id":242,"label":"MAT","start_offset":27,"end_offset":30}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":505,"text":"钴集中分布在刚果和澳大利亚。隔膜是技术壁垒较高的多孔材料，目前主要掌握在日韩企业手中。","entities":[{"id":239,"label":"MAT","start_offset":0,"end_offset":1},{"id":240,"label":"MAT","start_offset":14,"end_offset":16}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":506,"text":"动力电池的中游，主要是电芯、模组及电池包的制备及封装。下游主要是应用领域。","entities":[{"id":283,"label":"PAR","start_offset":11,"end_offset":13},{"id":284,"label":"PAR","start_offset":14,"end_offset":16},{"id":285,"label":"PAR","start_offset":17,"end_offset":20},{"id":339,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":0,"end_offset":4}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":507,"text":"1）磷酸铁锂电池或迎第二春2020年1-11月，三元锂电池共计装车32871.3MWh，磷酸铁锂电池装机17495.5MWh，","entities":[{"id":350,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":2,"end_offset":8},{"id":351,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":24,"end_offset":29},{"id":352,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":44,"end_offset":50}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":508,"text":"可以看出动力电池领域虽然仍是以三元为主、磷酸铁锂为辅的态势，但从增长率上看，磷酸铁锂电池在持续走高，占比率已经超过30%。","entities":[{"id":399,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":4,"end_offset":8},{"id":400,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":20,"end_offset":24},{"id":401,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":15,"end_offset":17},{"id":402,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":38,"end_offset":44}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":513,"text":"鉴于动力电池在电动汽车产业发展的重要性，我国在近年制定了动力电池的技术发展路线图，以能量密度、成本、寿命为主要指标，涵盖了BEV纯电及PHEV插电混合，","entities":[{"id":353,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":2,"end_offset":6},{"id":354,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":28,"end_offset":32}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":514,"text":"覆盖了正负极材料、隔膜及电解液等。小七在前文给大家介绍了什么是刀片电池，而随着新能源的不断发展，各整车企业也都开始意识到电池的重要性，纷纷将目光抛向了电池技术。","entities":[{"id":403,"label":"MAT","start_offset":3,"end_offset":8},{"id":404,"label":"MAT","start_offset":9,"end_offset":11},{"id":405,"label":"MAT","start_offset":12,"end_offset":15},{"id":406,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":31,"end_offset":35}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":515,"text":"继比亚迪刀片电池之后，又陆续诞生了一些新形式电池，例如广汽埃安的弹匣电池，岚图汽车的琥珀\/云母电池，长城汽车的大禹电池，上汽集团的魔方电池。","entities":[{"id":432,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":32,"end_offset":36},{"id":433,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":55,"end_offset":59},{"id":434,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":65,"end_offset":69},{"id":435,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":4,"end_offset":8}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":516,"text":"1、广汽埃安的弹匣电池为什么叫弹匣电池，主要还是因为在结构上它采用了弹匣安全舱的设计，其电池模组看上去就像一个个弹匣安置在电池包之中，","entities":[{"id":206,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":7,"end_offset":11},{"id":207,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":15,"end_offset":19},{"id":328,"label":"PAR","start_offset":34,"end_offset":39},{"id":329,"label":"PAR","start_offset":61,"end_offset":64}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":517,"text":"它将每个电池包里的单独电芯都独立在安全舱之内，这样就可以有效地阻隔热失控电芯的蔓延。除了结构上的设计优化，广汽埃安的弹匣电池还涵盖了四项核心技术，","entities":[{"id":246,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":58,"end_offset":62},{"id":247,"label":"PAR","start_offset":36,"end_offset":38},{"id":248,"label":"PAR","start_offset":4,"end_offset":7},{"id":249,"label":"PAR","start_offset":11,"end_offset":13},{"id":250,"label":"PAR","start_offset":17,"end_offset":20}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":518,"text":"包括超高耐热稳定的电芯、超强隔热的电池安全舱、极速降温三维冷却系统以及全时管控的第五代电池管理系统。","entities":[{"id":286,"label":"PAR","start_offset":9,"end_offset":11},{"id":287,"label":"PAR","start_offset":17,"end_offset":22},{"id":289,"label":"PAR","start_offset":27,"end_offset":33},{"id":290,"label":"PAR","start_offset":43,"end_offset":49}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":519,"text":"弹匣电池是有别于刀片电池的，刀片电池实质上是磷酸铁锂电池，相较于传统电池只是内部结构有所不同，其通过去掉电池模组，采用创新包封装技术，","entities":[{"id":355,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":0,"end_offset":4},{"id":356,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":8,"end_offset":12},{"id":357,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":14,"end_offset":18},{"id":358,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":22,"end_offset":28}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":520,"text":"在安全的前提下实现电池能量密度的增加，主要针对的还是磷酸铁锂电池。而弹匣电池并非特指某一种动力电池种类，它是一种电池系统安全技术，官方给出的解释为，这是一个专门提升动力电池安全性的系统性技术。","entities":[{"id":407,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":26,"end_offset":32},{"id":408,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":34,"end_offset":38},{"id":409,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":45,"end_offset":49},{"id":410,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":82,"end_offset":86}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":522,"text":"而是这两款电池中所采用的隔热材料颜色和形态酷似琥珀和云母。琥珀和云母电池的主要区别是三维隔热墙的材料及结构不同，琥珀电池的三维隔热墙技术，是在电池包内填充特殊有机硅复合材料，","entities":[{"id":208,"label":"PAR","start_offset":12,"end_offset":16},{"id":209,"label":"PAR","start_offset":42,"end_offset":47},{"id":210,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":56,"end_offset":60},{"id":211,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":32,"end_offset":36},{"id":212,"label":"MAT","start_offset":79,"end_offset":86}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":523,"text":"这种材料的特点是结合有机硅聚合物+低密度隔热材料+阻燃剂（1000℃以上），形成高效的隔热阻燃绝缘层，每个电芯单元像“琥珀”一样处于充分包裹中，也是将其命名为“琥珀”的原因。","entities":[{"id":251,"label":"MAT","start_offset":10,"end_offset":16},{"id":252,"label":"MAT","start_offset":17,"end_offset":24},{"id":253,"label":"MAT","start_offset":25,"end_offset":28},{"id":254,"label":"PAR","start_offset":53,"end_offset":55},{"id":335,"label":"PAR","start_offset":43,"end_offset":50}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":524,"text":"“云母” 电池系统三维隔热墙技术，是在电池包内加入层状Al-Si云母和气凝胶，且电芯和云母、气凝胶会像云母石一样层叠堆积，“云母”命名源于此。","entities":[{"id":292,"label":"PAR","start_offset":19,"end_offset":22},{"id":293,"label":"MAT","start_offset":27,"end_offset":34},{"id":294,"label":"MAT","start_offset":35,"end_offset":38},{"id":295,"label":"PAR","start_offset":40,"end_offset":42},{"id":296,"label":"MAT","start_offset":43,"end_offset":45},{"id":297,"label":"MAT","start_offset":46,"end_offset":49}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":525,"text":"根据官方信息显示，琥珀电池系统主要运用于纯电车型，而云母电池系统则会搭载于增程式车型上。","entities":[{"id":359,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":9,"end_offset":13},{"id":360,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":26,"end_offset":30}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":526,"text":"3、长城的大禹电池长城汽车的大禹电池，并没有根据电池形态或者隔热材料的形态命名，而是通过一种全新的“变堵为疏”的设计理念，取名为“大禹”。","entities":[{"id":411,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":5,"end_offset":9},{"id":412,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":14,"end_offset":18}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":527,"text":"大禹电池，简单来说就是万一发生热失控，将气流、火流按照设计通道安全疏导出电池包外，通过疏导的方式排出热量，进行“定向泄洪”。","entities":[{"id":436,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":0,"end_offset":4},{"id":437,"label":"PAR","start_offset":36,"end_offset":39}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":528,"text":"其核心技术就是通过“控”和“导”提升动力电池安全性，“控”方面实现电芯热阻隔、模组级阻隔、绝热材料对比。","entities":[{"id":330,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":18,"end_offset":22},{"id":331,"label":"PAR","start_offset":33,"end_offset":35}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":529,"text":"“导”方面采用灭火盒阻火设计和PACK定向排爆，通过定向排爆流场、温度场、阻火盒、传导传热四个方面实现排爆、降温、导热等。","entities":[{"id":255,"label":"PAR","start_offset":7,"end_offset":10},{"id":256,"label":"PAR","start_offset":15,"end_offset":19}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":530,"text":"大禹电池并非是材料的创新，它也不是一个电池包，而是系统性的集成技术，该技术可有效解决不同化学体系电芯发生热失控之后的起火、爆炸问题。","entities":[{"id":298,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":0,"end_offset":4},{"id":299,"label":"PAR","start_offset":19,"end_offset":22},{"id":300,"label":"PAR","start_offset":48,"end_offset":50}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":531,"text":"相比其他电池技术，大禹电池的适配性极强，可以兼容不同正极材料配比，如NCM811三元锂电池、三元锂电池体系的NCA（镍钴铝）电芯及无钴电芯等，以及不同技术线路的磷酸铁锂电池，都可以装载到大禹电池上。","entities":[{"id":361,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":9,"end_offset":13},{"id":362,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":34,"end_offset":45},{"id":363,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":46,"end_offset":51},{"id":364,"label":"PAR","start_offset":54,"end_offset":64},{"id":365,"label":"MAT","start_offset":58,"end_offset":61},{"id":366,"label":"PAR","start_offset":65,"end_offset":69},{"id":367,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":80,"end_offset":86},{"id":368,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":93,"end_offset":97}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":533,"text":"尺寸方面，魔方电池采用标准电池包，长宽统一，分别为1300mm、1690mm；高度有三种，分别为110mm、125mm和137mm。","entities":[{"id":438,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":5,"end_offset":9},{"id":439,"label":"PAR","start_offset":13,"end_offset":16}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":534,"text":"不同厚度的好处是，在保持统一的投影面积下，能够根据车型的定位，容纳不同的电芯，做成容量不同的电池包。","entities":[{"id":214,"label":"PAR","start_offset":36,"end_offset":38},{"id":215,"label":"PAR","start_offset":46,"end_offset":49}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":536,"text":"化学体系，魔方电池的电芯可以兼容不同化学体系，包括低能量密度的磷酸铁锂、钠离子、M3P等，中能量密度的三元电池5系、6系和高镍三元等，以及高能量密度的硅碳负极、半固态等都在应用范围之内。","entities":[{"id":301,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":5,"end_offset":9},{"id":302,"label":"PAR","start_offset":10,"end_offset":12},{"id":303,"label":"MAT","start_offset":31,"end_offset":35},{"id":304,"label":"MAT","start_offset":36,"end_offset":39},{"id":305,"label":"MAT","start_offset":40,"end_offset":43},{"id":340,"label":"PAR","start_offset":75,"end_offset":79},{"id":341,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":51,"end_offset":55}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":537,"text":"除了尺寸及化学体系的灵活优势外，上汽的魔方电池还有一个特点就是能够躺平。目前，在市面上大多数品牌的电池都采用了铝壳方形电芯，而它们大部分都采用传统的立式布局，但魔方电池相比它们而言，则采用了全新的躺式布局。","entities":[{"id":369,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":19,"end_offset":23},{"id":370,"label":"PAR","start_offset":55,"end_offset":61},{"id":371,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":80,"end_offset":84}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":539,"text":"由于采用了躺式电芯结构布局电池绝大部分空间都可以用来容纳有效的电化学材料 ，因此相比竞品而言上汽魔方电池在各个容量电池包的体积效率转换和重量效率转换都更为出色。","entities":[{"id":440,"label":"PAR","start_offset":7,"end_offset":9},{"id":441,"label":"PAR","start_offset":57,"end_offset":60},{"id":442,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":48,"end_offset":52}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":577,"text":"虽然动力电池有几层防护，但是就怕出现意外情况，随着电池护板上大部分螺丝的拆除，拿掉最突出的一块护板","entities":[{"id":480,"label":"PAR","start_offset":25,"end_offset":29},{"id":481,"label":"PAR","start_offset":47,"end_offset":49}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":574,"text":"为了拆解方便，大哥直接用刀片沿着胶水粘住的部分切开，拿掉这一层以后看到的就是整个电池包的金属护板","entities":[{"id":560,"label":"PAR","start_offset":40,"end_offset":43},{"id":561,"label":"PAR","start_offset":44,"end_offset":48}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":577,"text":"虽然动力电池有几层防护，但是就怕出现意外情况，随着电池护板上大部分螺丝的拆除，拿掉最突出的一块护板","entities":[{"id":480,"label":"PAR","start_offset":25,"end_offset":29},{"id":481,"label":"PAR","start_offset":47,"end_offset":49}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":580,"text":"大哥用尖嘴钳熟练地将电池护板翘起来一脚，可以看出金属护板粘的很牢，翘起来还是比较费劲","entities":[{"id":562,"label":"PAR","start_offset":10,"end_offset":14},{"id":563,"label":"PAR","start_offset":24,"end_offset":28}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":582,"text":"拿掉最上面的金属护板以后，就能看到16个电池组整齐的排列在电池包内，并且在每个电池组上还有一块金属护板","entities":[{"id":443,"label":"PAR","start_offset":6,"end_offset":10},{"id":444,"label":"PAR","start_offset":20,"end_offset":23},{"id":445,"label":"PAR","start_offset":29,"end_offset":32},{"id":446,"label":"PAR","start_offset":39,"end_offset":42},{"id":447,"label":"PAR","start_offset":47,"end_offset":51}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":583,"text":"要想将电池组取下来，第一件要做的事就是拔掉电池组的电源，然后松掉固定电池组的两个螺丝","entities":[{"id":482,"label":"PAR","start_offset":3,"end_offset":6},{"id":483,"label":"PAR","start_offset":21,"end_offset":24},{"id":484,"label":"PAR","start_offset":34,"end_offset":37}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":584,"text":"最后就可以使用工具将电池组翘起来了，接下来用老哥的第一视角看看取下电池组的全过程","entities":[{"id":503,"label":"PAR","start_offset":10,"end_offset":13},{"id":504,"label":"PAR","start_offset":33,"end_offset":36}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":586,"text":"接下来老哥拆掉的黑色接头，应该是电池管理系统的控制线，翘起电池组以后剪掉的黑色管道是电池冷却管道","entities":[{"id":564,"label":"PAR","start_offset":16,"end_offset":22},{"id":565,"label":"PAR","start_offset":29,"end_offset":32},{"id":566,"label":"PAR","start_offset":42,"end_offset":48}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":588,"text":"当单节电池出现温度过高时，保险丝会自动熔断，保护整个电池组","entities":[{"id":448,"label":"PAR","start_offset":13,"end_offset":16},{"id":449,"label":"PAR","start_offset":26,"end_offset":29}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":590,"text":"在拆掉最后两个电池组以后，今天的拆解就差不多全部完成了","entities":[{"id":505,"label":"PAR","start_offset":7,"end_offset":10}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":591,"text":"说到电动车的电池，很多人一定都听说过比亚迪的刀片电池和特斯拉的4680电池","entities":[{"id":528,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":22,"end_offset":26},{"id":529,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":31,"end_offset":37}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":594,"text":"我们今天就借着4680和刀片电池的对比，仔细研究一下动力电池的材料结构集成以及发展趋势","entities":[{"id":450,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":7,"end_offset":11},{"id":451,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":12,"end_offset":16}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":596,"text":"一片正极极片，一片负极极片，中间夹着一层隔膜以及电解液，然后在正负极片的一端会各带有一个吉尔用料，把电压传导出去","entities":[{"id":506,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":6},{"id":507,"label":"PAR","start_offset":9,"end_offset":13},{"id":508,"label":"MAT","start_offset":20,"end_offset":22},{"id":509,"label":"MAT","start_offset":24,"end_offset":27},{"id":510,"label":"PAR","start_offset":31,"end_offset":35}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":597,"text":"所以放电和充电的过程就是，电子穿过隔膜和电解液，在正负极之间流动的过程","entities":[{"id":530,"label":"MAT","start_offset":17,"end_offset":19},{"id":531,"label":"MAT","start_offset":20,"end_offset":23},{"id":532,"label":"PAR","start_offset":25,"end_offset":28}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":600,"text":"指的都是电池的正极材料，刀片电池的正极材料使用的是磷酸铁锂，而4680电池可以使用三元锂或者磷酸铁锂，到底哪种材料更好呢","entities":[{"id":452,"label":"PAR","start_offset":7,"end_offset":9},{"id":453,"label":"PAR","start_offset":17,"end_offset":19},{"id":454,"label":"MAT","start_offset":25,"end_offset":29},{"id":455,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":31,"end_offset":37},{"id":456,"label":"MAT","start_offset":41,"end_offset":44},{"id":457,"label":"MAT","start_offset":46,"end_offset":50}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":601,"text":"首先三元锂电芯的能量密度显著高于磷酸铁锂，根据宾夕法尼亚大学王朝安院士团队的论文，单体的FP电池，也就是磷酸铁锂电池","entities":[{"id":486,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":7},{"id":487,"label":"MAT","start_offset":16,"end_offset":20},{"id":488,"label":"MAT","start_offset":2,"end_offset":5},{"id":489,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":52,"end_offset":58},{"id":490,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":44,"end_offset":48}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":602,"text":"能量密度大概是180瓦时每公斤，而三元锂电池的能量密度，可以超过250瓦时每公斤","entities":[{"id":511,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":17,"end_offset":22}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":603,"text":"同时三元锂的低温放电性能要优于磷酸铁锂，在没有电池加热和保温的情况下，零度的FP电池的有效续航只有MC62电池的58%","entities":[{"id":533,"label":"MAT","start_offset":2,"end_offset":5},{"id":534,"label":"MAT","start_offset":15,"end_offset":19},{"id":535,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":38,"end_offset":42},{"id":536,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":49,"end_offset":55}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":606,"text":"FP电芯的成本普遍比三元锂低20%以上，根据20年的研究报告，FP电芯的循环寿命最高可以达到9000次","entities":[{"id":458,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":4},{"id":459,"label":"MAT","start_offset":10,"end_offset":13},{"id":460,"label":"PAR","start_offset":31,"end_offset":35}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":607,"text":"而三元锂最高只能达到2500次。除此之外，三元锂的热安全性是要差于磷酸铁锂的","entities":[{"id":491,"label":"MAT","start_offset":1,"end_offset":4},{"id":492,"label":"MAT","start_offset":21,"end_offset":24},{"id":493,"label":"MAT","start_offset":33,"end_offset":37}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":608,"text":"三元锂的高温分解温度更低，同时自放热超过500焦耳每克，而FP只有不到150焦耳。","entities":[{"id":512,"label":"MAT","start_offset":0,"end_offset":3},{"id":513,"label":"MAT","start_offset":29,"end_offset":31}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":609,"text":"不仅如此，三元锂受热分解时会释放出氧气，而自放热和氧气的释放，都会让三元锂更容易出现热失控风险","entities":[{"id":537,"label":"MAT","start_offset":5,"end_offset":8},{"id":538,"label":"MAT","start_offset":34,"end_offset":37}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":612,"text":"而三元锂的电动车，就更推荐充电到90%以下，避免对电动车的性能造成长期的影响","entities":[{"id":461,"label":"MAT","start_offset":1,"end_offset":4}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":614,"text":"三元锂在能量密度和低温性能上拥有优势，但同时受到高成本的限制，更适用于关注于性能的中高端车型","entities":[{"id":514,"label":"MAT","start_offset":0,"end_offset":3}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":615,"text":"而磷酸铁锂拥有出色的成本和寿命优势，但同时受限于能量密度和低温性能，因此更适用于中低端车型和储能场景。","entities":[{"id":539,"label":"MAT","start_offset":1,"end_offset":5}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":618,"text":"除了4680对应的圆柱电池和刀片，电池对应的方形电池这两种分类。","entities":[{"id":462,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":2,"end_offset":6},{"id":463,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":9,"end_offset":13},{"id":465,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":22,"end_offset":26}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":624,"text":"然后在正负极的那一端会引出一段金属导体，也被称为吉尔，这里我们需要记住两个重要的概念，卷绕封装以及吉尔那作为对比","entities":[{"id":466,"label":"PAR","start_offset":3,"end_offset":6}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":630,"text":"它拧紧的力矩是78牛米，第二个我们来看动力电池的规格，首先来看水冷，在帝豪EV300当中，动力电池的类型是三元锂离子电池，","entities":[{"id":467,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":53,"end_offset":60}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":633,"text":"电池的种类为磷酸铁锂动力电池，电池组的额定电压为346伏，峰值功率为150千瓦，它能够持续十秒，额定功率为50千瓦，","entities":[{"id":540,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":6,"end_offset":14}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":636,"text":"使用有机电解质，动力电池的总成安装在车体的下部，动力电池的组成部件还包括各模组总成，cs采集系统，电池控制单元b，mu，","entities":[{"id":468,"label":"MAT","start_offset":2,"end_offset":7},{"id":469,"label":"PAR","start_offset":37,"end_offset":41},{"id":470,"label":"PAR","start_offset":42,"end_offset":48},{"id":471,"label":"PAR","start_offset":49,"end_offset":55}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":637,"text":"电压分配单元b，box，还有维维修开关等部件，第三个我们来看动力电池的模组，首先我们来看单体电池，","entities":[{"id":494,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":6}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":638,"text":"单体电池我们可以理解为一节5号电池，它是直接将化学能转化为电能的基本单元装置，包括电极隔膜，电解质外壳和端子电池的单体，","entities":[{"id":516,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":4},{"id":517,"label":"PAR","start_offset":41,"end_offset":45},{"id":518,"label":"PAR","start_offset":46,"end_offset":51}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":639,"text":"被设计成可以充电，当前在国内，电动电动车电池技术主要使用的是三元锂电池，和磷酸铁锂电池，首先来看三元锂电池，","entities":[{"id":541,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":30,"end_offset":35},{"id":542,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":37,"end_offset":43}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":642,"text":"它可实现电能与化学能之间的直接转换，第二个我们来看电池模组，将一倍以上的电池单体，按照串联并联或者串并联的方式组合，","entities":[{"id":472,"label":"PAR","start_offset":25,"end_offset":29},{"id":473,"label":"PAR","start_offset":36,"end_offset":40}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":644,"text":"我们是用若干节的电池串联在一起，吉利帝豪EV300的电池模组，由七个1P5S模块，和十个1P6S模块组合而成，","entities":[{"id":520,"label":"PAR","start_offset":34,"end_offset":40},{"id":521,"label":"PAR","start_offset":44,"end_offset":50}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":648,"text":"COS采集系统，将相关的信息上报电池控制单元，也就是BMU，并根据BMU的指令执行单体电压的一个均衡，","entities":[{"id":474,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":7},{"id":475,"label":"PAR","start_offset":16,"end_offset":22},{"id":476,"label":"PAR","start_offset":26,"end_offset":29},{"id":477,"label":"PAR","start_offset":33,"end_offset":36}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":649,"text":"第五我们来学习电池控制单元BMU，它安装于动力电池总成的内部，是电池管理系统的核心部件，电池控制单元BMU能够将电池电压，","entities":[{"id":495,"label":"PAR","start_offset":7,"end_offset":13},{"id":496,"label":"PAR","start_offset":13,"end_offset":16},{"id":497,"label":"PAR","start_offset":44,"end_offset":50},{"id":498,"label":"PAR","start_offset":50,"end_offset":53}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":651,"text":"它安装在动力电池总成的正负极输出端，由高压正极继电器，高压负极继电器，预充继电器，电流传感器和预充电阻等组成，","entities":[{"id":543,"label":"PAR","start_offset":19,"end_offset":26},{"id":544,"label":"PAR","start_offset":27,"end_offset":34},{"id":545,"label":"PAR","start_offset":35,"end_offset":40},{"id":546,"label":"PAR","start_offset":41,"end_offset":46},{"id":547,"label":"PAR","start_offset":47,"end_offset":51},{"id":548,"label":"PAR","start_offset":11,"end_offset":14}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":655,"text":"BMS可以将动力电池相关参数上报给VCU，也就是整车控制器，并由整车控制器控制，动力电池的充电和放电功率，","entities":[{"id":499,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":3}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":656,"text":"电池管理系统的基本结构，它的组成按性质可分为硬件和软件，按功能分为数据采集单元和控制单元，","entities":[{"id":522,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":6}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":657,"text":"BMS的硬件主要由主板重板及高压盒，还包括采集电压线，电流温度等数据的电子器件，BMCBMS的软件主要是监测电池的电压，","entities":[{"id":549,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":3},{"id":550,"label":"PAR","start_offset":9,"end_offset":13},{"id":551,"label":"PAR","start_offset":14,"end_offset":17},{"id":553,"label":"PAR","start_offset":40,"end_offset":43},{"id":554,"label":"PAR","start_offset":43,"end_offset":46}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":660,"text":"以及电子电气元件以外的辅助元器件，比如密封条，绝缘材料等，接下来是电气原理的框图，我们以动力电池模块为核心，","entities":[{"id":478,"label":"PAR","start_offset":19,"end_offset":22},{"id":479,"label":"PAR","start_offset":23,"end_offset":27}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":662,"text":"直流充电设备发送充电唤醒信号给BMS，也就是电池管理系统，BMS根据动力电池的可充电功率，向直流充电设备发送充电电流指令，","entities":[{"id":524,"label":"PAR","start_offset":15,"end_offset":18},{"id":525,"label":"PAR","start_offset":22,"end_offset":28},{"id":526,"label":"PAR","start_offset":29,"end_offset":32},{"id":527,"label":"PAR","start_offset":0,"end_offset":6}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":663,"text":"同时BMS吸核系统，高压正继电器和高压负继电器，动力电池开始充电，在快充的时候，我们48分钟可以充满，","entities":[{"id":555,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":5},{"id":556,"label":"PAR","start_offset":10,"end_offset":16},{"id":557,"label":"PAR","start_offset":17,"end_offset":23}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":669,"text":"辅助控制器，ACM将持续对电源蓄电池的电压进行监控，当电压低于设定值时，ACM将唤醒BMS电池管理系统，","entities":[{"id":558,"label":"PAR","start_offset":6,"end_offset":9},{"id":559,"label":"PAR","start_offset":42,"end_offset":51}],"relations":[],"Comments":[]}
{"id":858,"text":"根据单体电池封装形式不同，可以分为圆柱电芯、方形电芯及软包电芯。","entities":[{"id":931,"label":"PAR","start_offset":2,"end_offset":6},{"id":932,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":17,"end_offset":21},{"id":933,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":22,"end_offset":26},{"id":934,"label":"TYPE","start_offset":27,"end_offset":31}],"relations":[{"id":164,"from_id":931,"to_id":932,"type":"包括"},{"id":165,"from_id":931,"to_id":933,"type":"包括"},{"id":166,"from_id":931,"to_id":934,"type":"包括"}],"Comments":[]}
